name: Atlassian Jira Software Icons
description:
I love so much using the Atlassian products. Especially in Jira and Confluence, I needed more icons and standards between icons to differentiate many projects and spaces from each other visually. Then... ta-da.


The JIRA Software project icons are also prepared to be used in Confluence Spaces.


- Atlassian Colors

- JIRA Project Icons

- JIRA Issue Type Icons

- Custom JIRA Project Icons

- Custom JIRA Issue Type Icons
